<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.1//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml11/DTD/xhtml11.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<head>
		<title>WOFF 2.0: Authoring Tool Test Suite</title>
		<style type="text/css">
			@import "resources/index.css";
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>WOFF 2.0: Authoring Tool Test Suite (24 tests)</h1>
		<div class="mainNote">
			The files used in these test can be obtained individually <a href="../xhtml1">here</a> or as a single zip file <a href="AuthoringToolTestFonts.zip">here</a>.
		</div>
		<div class="mainNote">
			The tests in this suite represent SFNT data to be used for WOFF
			conversion without any alteration or correction. An authoring tool
			may allow the explicit or silent modification and/or correction of
			SFNT data. In such a case, the tests in this suite that are labeled
			as "should not convert" may be converted, so long as the problems
			in the files have been corrected. In that case, there is no longer
			any access to the "input font" as defined in the WOFF specification,
			so the bitwise identical tests should be skipped.
		</div>

		<h2 class="testCategory">SFNT Table Directory Tests</h2>
		<div class="testCategoryNote">
			These files are valid SFNTs that excercise conversion of the table directory.
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledirectory-order-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledirectory-order-001">tabledirectory-order-001</a>: Valid Font Collection With Unsorted fonts</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection with fonts not in alphabetical order. WOFF creation process must reserve the font order.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledirectory-order-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustPreserveFontOrder">conform-mustPreserveFontOrder</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledirectory-collection-index-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledirectory-collection-index-001">tabledirectory-collection-index-001</a>: Valid Font Collection</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection. WOFF creation process must record the index of the matching TableDirectoryEntry into the CollectionFontEntry for each font.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledirectory-collection-index-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustRecordCollectionEntryIndex">conform-mustRecordCollectionEntryIndex</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledirectory-knowntags-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledirectory-knowntags-001">tabledirectory-knowntags-001</a>: Valid TTF SFNT With All Tables Known</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font with all tables known. Output WOFF2 table directory must use known table flag for all tables in the font.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledirectory-knowntags-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustUseKnownTags">conform-mustUseKnownTags</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledirectory-knowntags-002">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledirectory-knowntags-002">tabledirectory-knowntags-002</a>: Valid TTF SFNT With Some Tables Unknown</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font with some tables unknown. Output WOFF2 table directory must use known table flag for known tables.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledirectory-knowntags-002-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustUseKnownTags">conform-mustUseKnownTags</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2 class="testCategory">SFNT Table Data Tests</h2>
		<div class="testCategoryNote">
			These files are valid SFNTs that excercise conversion of the table data.
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-dsig-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-dsig-001">tabledata-dsig-001</a>: CFF SFNT With DSIG Table</h3>
				<p>The CFF flavored SFNT has a DSIG table. (Note: this is not a valid DSIG. It should not be used for testing anything other than the presence of the table after the conversion process.) The process of converting to WOFF should remove the DSIG table.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-dsig-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustRemoveDSIG">conform-mustRemoveDSIG</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-dsig-002">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-dsig-002">tabledata-dsig-002</a>: TTF SFNT With DSIG Table</h3>
				<p>The TFF flavored SFNT has a DSIG table. (Note: this is not a valid DSIG. It should not be used for testing anything other than the presence of the table after the conversion process.) The process of converting to WOFF should remove the DSIG table.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-dsig-002-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustRemoveDSIG">conform-mustRemoveDSIG</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-bit11-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-bit11-001">tabledata-bit11-001</a>: Valid CFF SFNT For Bit 11</h3>
				<p>The bit 11 of the head table flags must be set for CFF flavored SFNT.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-bit11-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustSetBit11">conform-mustSetBit11</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-bit11-002">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-bit11-002">tabledata-bit11-002</a>: Valid TTF SFNT For Bit 11</h3>
				<p>The bit 11 of the head table flags must be set for TTF flavored SFNT.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-bit11-002-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustSetBit11">conform-mustSetBit11</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-transform-glyf-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-transform-glyf-001">tabledata-transform-glyf-001</a>: Valid TTF SFNT For Glyph BBox Calculation 1</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font containing glyphs with the calculated bounding box matches the encoded one, the transformed glyf table in the output WOFF font must have bboxBitmap with all values as 0 and empty bboxStream.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-transform-glyf-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustCalculateOmitBBoxValues">conform-mustCalculateOmitBBoxValues</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-transform-glyf-002">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-transform-glyf-002">tabledata-transform-glyf-002</a>: Valid TTF SFNT For Glyph BBox Calculation 2</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font containing glyphs with the calculated bounding box differing from the encoded one, the transformed glyf table in the output WOFF font must have bboxBitmap and bboxStream set with the encoded bounding boxes.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-transform-glyf-002-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustCalculateSetBBoxValues">conform-mustCalculateSetBBoxValues</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-transform-glyf-003">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-transform-glyf-003">tabledata-transform-glyf-003</a>: Valid TTF SFNT For Glyph BBox Calculation 3</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font containing glyphs with the calculated bounding box differing from the encoded one and a composite glyph, the transformed glyf table in the output WOFF font must have bboxBitmap and bboxStream set with the encoded bounding boxes.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-transform-glyf-003-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustSetCompositeBBoxValues">conform-mustSetCompositeBBoxValues</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-transform-glyf-004">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-transform-glyf-004">tabledata-transform-glyf-004</a>: Invalid TTF SFNT With Empty Glyph BBox 1</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font containing a glyph with zero contours and non-zero bounding box values.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-transform-glyf-004-shouldconvert">No</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustRejectNonEmptyBBox">conform-mustRejectNonEmptyBBox</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-transform-glyf-005">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-transform-glyf-005">tabledata-transform-glyf-005</a>: Invalid TTF SFNT With Empty Glyph BBox 2</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font containing a glyph with zero contours and zero bounding box values, the transformed glyf table in the output WOFF font must have bboxBitmap with all values as 0 and empty bboxStream.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-transform-glyf-005-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustClearEmptyBBox">conform-mustClearEmptyBBox</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="tabledata-transform-hmtx-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#tabledata-transform-hmtx-001">tabledata-transform-hmtx-001</a>: Valid TTF SFNT For Glyph LSB Elemination 1</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT font containing two proportional and two monospaced glyphs with left side bearings matching the Xmin values of each corresponding glyph bonding box. The hmtx table must be transformed with version 1 transform, eliminating both lsb[] and leftSideBearing[] arrays with corresponding Flags bits set.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="tabledata-transform-hmtx-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustEliminateLSBs">conform-mustEliminateLSBs</a> 
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustCheckLeftSideBearings">conform-mustCheckLeftSideBearings</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2 class="testCategory">SFNT Collection Tests</h2>
		<div class="testCategoryNote">
			These files are valid SFNTs that excercise conversion of font collections.
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-sharing-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-sharing-001">collection-sharing-001</a>: Valid Font Collection With No Duplicate Tables</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection with all tables being shared, output WOFF font must not contain any duplicate tables.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-sharing-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustNotDuplicateTables">conform-mustNotDuplicateTables</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-sharing-002">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-sharing-002">collection-sharing-002</a>: Valid Font Collection With Shared Glyf/Loca</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection containing two fonts sharing the same glyf and loca tables.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-sharing-002-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustVerifyGlyfLocaShared">conform-mustVerifyGlyfLocaShared</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-sharing-003">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-sharing-003">collection-sharing-003</a>: Valid Font Collection With Shared And Unshared Glyf/Loca</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection containing three fonts, two of them sharing the same glyf and loca tables and the third using different glyf and loca tables.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-sharing-003-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustNotDuplicateTables">conform-mustNotDuplicateTables</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-sharing-004">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-sharing-004">collection-sharing-004</a>: Invalid Font Collection With Unshared Loca</h3>
				<p>An invalid TTF flavored SFNT collection containing two fonts sharing glyf but not loca table.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-sharing-004-shouldconvert">No</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustRejectSingleGlyfLocaShared">conform-mustRejectSingleGlyfLocaShared</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-sharing-005">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-sharing-005">collection-sharing-005</a>: Invalid Font Collection With Unshared Glyf</h3>
				<p>An invalid TTF flavored SFNT collection containing two fonts sharing loca but not glyf table.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-sharing-005-shouldconvert">No</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustRejectSingleGlyfLocaShared">conform-mustRejectSingleGlyfLocaShared</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-sharing-006">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-sharing-006">collection-sharing-006</a>: Font Collection With Single Shared Table</h3>
				<p>A valid TTF flavored SFNT collection containing two fonts sharing only the cmap table.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-sharing-006-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustEmitSingleEntryDirectory">conform-mustEmitSingleEntryDirectory</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-transform-glyf-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-transform-glyf-001">collection-transform-glyf-001</a>: Valid Font Collection With Multiple Glyf/Loca</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection with multiple unshared glyf and loca tables, all of them must be transformed in the output WOFF font.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-transform-glyf-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustTransformMultipleGlyfLoca">conform-mustTransformMultipleGlyfLoca</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-transform-hmtx-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-transform-hmtx-001">collection-transform-hmtx-001</a>: Valid Font Collection With Unshared Glyf And Shared Hmtx 1</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection with multiple unshared glyf tanles and one shared hmtx table where xMin and LSB of all glyphs is 0.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-transform-hmtx-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustCheckLSBAllGlyfTables">conform-mustCheckLSBAllGlyfTables</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-transform-hmtx-002">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-transform-hmtx-002">collection-transform-hmtx-002</a>: Valid Font Collection With Unshared Glyf And Shared Hmtx 2</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection with multiple unshared glyf tanles and one shared hmtx table where LSB of all glyphs is 0, but xMin in some glyphs in the second glyf table is not 0.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-transform-hmtx-002-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustNotApplyLSBTransformForOTC">conform-mustNotApplyLSBTransformForOTC</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="testCase" id="collection-pairing-001">
			<div class="testCaseOverview">
				<h3><a href="#collection-pairing-001">collection-pairing-001</a>: Valid Font Collection With Glyf/Loca Pairs</h3>
				<p>TTF flavored SFNT collection with multiple unshared glyf and loca tables, glyf and loca tables from each font must be paired in the output WOFF font.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="testCaseDetails">
					<p>Should Convert to WOFF: <span id="collection-pairing-001-shouldconvert">Yes</span></p>
					<p>
						<a href="http://dev.w3.org/webfonts/WOFF2/spec/#conform-mustReorderGlyfLoca">conform-mustReorderGlyfLoca</a> 
					</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>